<% content_for :title, "GDPR | DevDeBizz" %>

<%= render "page_header",
  eyebrow: "GDPR",
  title_html: 'Data protection & <span class="home-display-accent">GDPR compliance</span>'.html_safe,
  subtitle: "Our commitment to user data privacy rights under General Data Protection Regulation." %>

<section class="py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-2 md:px-0">
    <div class="home-glass home-card-3d rounded-[32px] p-8 md:p-12 space-y-8 text-[#081849]/80 leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#081849] mb-3">Our position on privacy</h2>
        <p>We believe in absolute data minimization. We only collect the minimal amount of personal details required to reply to your service requests or process invoice checkout flows.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#081849] mb-3">Your rights under GDPR</h2>
        <p>If you reside within the European Economic Area (EEA), you possess the following rights regarding your personal information:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Right of Access:</strong> You may request a complete copy of any personal data we hold about you.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Rectification:</strong> You can request that we update or correct inaccurate personal details.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Erasure:</strong> You can request that we permanently delete your personal information (the \"right to be forgotten\").</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Portability:</strong> You can request that we export your data in a structured, standard format.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#081849] mb-3">Submit a request</h2>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, please submit a request to <%= link_to contact_email, "mailto:#{contact_email}", class: "font-semibold underline text-[#213885]" %>. We process and reply to all data rights requests within 30 days.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
